Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}嗨，我现在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}请在“哔”一声之后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}最后的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}简直红得像血一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}副司令被绑架了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是在离现在两小时前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}最后在西部第 8 管区失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那不是我们自己的地盘么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你们情报部在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}内部有密探及内应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我们中了那人的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}可以把情报 2 课耍弄的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}加持良治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}他被认定是这次事件的主谋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以，你们才会到我这里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}您能这么快理解真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}被迫要去怀疑作战课长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}作为同事，我们也感到不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不过这也是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}考虑到他和我的经历，这或许是理所当然的处置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}非常感谢您的合作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}好久不见了，基尔议长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真是粗暴的欢迎方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我没必要为失礼而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}为了跟你好好谈谈这是必须的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真是一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}就不管我这里方不方便么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}因为这个议题很紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}这是不得已的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}希望你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}没想到不是委员会，而是 SEELE 亲自出面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我们没有打算创造新的神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}希望你能合作，冬月老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}冬月老师…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}冬月老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}老师待会有没有空？去鸭川喝点啤酒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}又要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}亮子她们说跟老师一起的话，她们就答应过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}教授也说您偶尔也得出席一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}偶尔像这样在外面喝酒也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你虽然很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不过也不能忽视与别人的交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}对了，冬月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}生物工程系那边有个学生写了一篇很有意思的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是个姓碇的学生，你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}碇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我提到你的事情时，她说一定要见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}相信她不久便会联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}麻烦你关照一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}碇君是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我知道了
